                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The document that follows shows the different forms of adherence used by this
                    Government to bring into force on the part of the United States major agreements
                    respecting the United Nations and its specialized agencies, 1945–1949. The list
                    has relevance also as affording a comprehensive view of the United Nations
                    treaty system five years after the United Nations Conference on International
                    Organization held at San Francisco, April 25–June 26, 1945.</p>
            </div>
